# **Capra Skip**

The&nbsp;**Capra Skip**&nbsp;is a&nbsp;sequence break&nbsp;in&nbsp;Dark Souls Remastered&nbsp;that allows the player to skip the door entrance to the Depths (and thus killing Capra to obtain the normally [necessary key](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/key-to-the-depths)) by getting&nbsp;[Deathcam](/darksouls/deathcam)&nbsp;in lower Undead Burg or by using the ladder method.

The deathcam method was found by Kahmul78 and CapitaineToinon in January 2017 and is not really used anymore because of the ladder method being a lot faster and easier .

## External Resources

- Deathcam method [https://youtu.be/XkxEqdG3SPw](https://youtu.be/XkxEqdG3SPw) by CapitaineToinon on YouTube.
- Ladder method tutorial [https://youtu.be/Fvz4MHZ620E](https://youtu.be/Fvz4MHZ620E) by San on YouTube.
